::Magmatron::

    He looked at the Key with the Autobot symbol on it. He grinned. He 
transformed to Robot mode. He snatched the key from Bobertron.
    "Thank you for the Key Bobertron." He put it on a table and turned away. 
"On second thought." He picked up the Key and snapped it. "THIS IS NOT IN MY 
PLANS!! Now leave, I have plans to attend."
    As Bobertron left Magmatron looked on one of his computer consols. It 
showed the Key to the Ark on it. "It's not in my plans, yet."
